fulltitle: The Maestros of Lodz Tango Salon Festival 2014 – Mariposita
title: The Maestros of Lodz Tango Salon Festival 2014 – Mariposita
_filename: The Maestros of Lodz Tango Salon Festival 2014 – Mariposita-H6B3VdPN3sw.mp4
description:
The Maestros of the 4th Łódź Tango Salon Festival 2014 dance “Mariposita” played live by Solo Tango Orquesta, sung by Ariel Ardit, in Lodz, Poland.

The maestros are
Maria Ines Bogado and Sebastian Jimenez
Stefania Colina and Juan Martin Carrara
Roxana Suarez and Sebastian Achaval
Josefina Bermudez Avila and Fabian Peralta

If you love Tango videos, help us create more on
